name: Jack'O'Lantern
description:
An Irish myth about Stingy Jack. He who tricked the Devil for his own monetary gain. When Jack died, he was denied from both Heaven & Hell, so he was forced to roam the earth for eternity. 

People started to carve demonic faces out of pumpkins to frighten away Jack’s wandering soul. 

Have you gotten your Jack 'O' Lantern yet? Or are you gonna let Stingy Jack come right into your house &...
